  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine the safety and efficacy of acupuncture in the
      treatment of moderate to severe dry eye by replicating the study design of the previous
      protocol and to see the study through to its completion.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
